Pagination:
breaking a lot oif info into small chuncks
Instead of sending all data, we send data in small chunks (pages)
With pagination
→ API returns only:
Page 0 → 10 records
Page 1 → next 10
Page 2 → next 10

What is DTP Pattern:
 is a pattern used to transfer data  b/n s/w application subsystem.
it's a simple java classes 
Lighweight


Why we need DTO in SB
To prevent exposing sensitive data
Send only required fields to the client


Steps:
1. Create DTO package
2. Create 2 classes one in RequestDTO another one is ResponseDTO
3. Create the mapper package where we woll convert from RequestDTO yo entity and entity to ResponseDTO.


